import styled from "styled-components"
import {FaInstagram,FaFacebook,FaPinterest,FaTwitter,FaSearch} from "react-icons/fa"
import {Avatar} from "@material-ui/core"
import {globalStyle} from "../../global/globalStyle"
export const Nav = styled.nav`
${globalStyle};
height:80px;
position:fiex;
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
grid-template-rows:80px

`
export const NavIcons = styled.div`
${globalStyle};
justify-content:end;

`
export const Fb = styled(FaFacebook)``
export const Insta = styled(FaInstagram)`` 
export const Twit = styled(FaTwitter)``
export const Pin = styled(FaPinterest)``
export const NavItems = styled.div``
export const NavItem = styled.div``
export const NavRight = styled.div``
export const AvatarImg = styled(Avatar)``
export const Search = styled(FaSearch)``
